              {
                "lang_tag": "ui7_kitdevice_6211_step_4_01",
                "text": "Turn on the main power to the Nano Switch.<br>\nPress or flip the wall switch connected to the (S1) input of the Nano Switch once. If you don't have an external wall switch connected to the (S1) input, carefully press (voltage will be present on terminals) the Action Button once on your Nano Switch to begin the pairing process.<br>\nThe LED will blink green for a few seconds then turn solid indicating pairing is successful."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "static_group": 2,
            "group_text": [
              {
                "lang_tag": "ui7_kitdevice_6211_step_4_11",
                "text": "If the LED on your Nano Switch turns red for 2 seconds and then returns to a colorful gradient (changing colors), and isn't detected in 60 seconds then click the 'Retry' button below to begin un-pairing it."
              }
            ]
          }
